---
// src/pages/team.astro
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Team | Cloud Identity Summit</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 font-sans antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- Einheitliche Navigation -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16">
                <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">CIS</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-white tracking-wide">Cloud Identity Summit</span>
                </a>

                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8 text-sm font-medium">
                    <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition">2026</a>
                    <a href="/archive" class="hover:text-white transition">Archive</a>
                    <a href="/team" class="text-blue-400">Team</a>
                    <a href="/sponsors" class="hover:text-white transition">Sponsors</a>
                    <a href="/code-of-conduct" class="hover:text-white transition">CoC</a>
                    <a href="/tickets" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/20">🎟 Tickets</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow">
        <div class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">About Us</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-8">The Team</h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-16">
            We from the Azure Meetup Bonn Team are cloud affine speakers who have fun organizing and participating in various community events. Our new project is the Cloud Identity Summit. At this event, we want to offer a platform for people interested in one of our main topics - identity.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2"><a href="https://www.cloud-architekt.net/" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">Thomas Naunheim</a></h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Thomas is our identity professional and has been dealing with the different facets of the Azure Active Directory for a long time. He is also a top speaker and has already given numerous presentations on the various identity features.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2"><a href="https://twitter.com/renedelamotte" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">René Wasel</a></h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    René is our community professional and can be found at numerous events. He is also part of the organizing team of Office 365 Cologne and the strong support in the background.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2"><a href="https://www.reimling.eu" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">Gregor Reimling</a></h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Gregor is very busy with Azure projects and shares his knowledge in this area with the community. He can be found at numerous events and is burning for the community.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-900 bg-slate-950 py-10 mt-auto">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 text-sm text-slate-500">
            <span>© 2026 Cloud Identity Summit</span>
            <div class="flex gap-8">
                <a href="/impressum" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Impressum</a>
                <a href="/datenschutz" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Datenschutz</a>
                <a href="/code-of-conduct" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Code of Conduct</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>